current.title: AI1
current.about:
All made on Udio

(RHYTHMS OF UNITY LYRICS)

[Intro]
Whirls of sound, dancing wild, (음악의 들판이 꾸밀다)
Crosswind turntable tales (στιγμιαία ηχογραφήση)
Floating rhythm's magic spell, (魔法のリズムに浮かんで)

[Verse]
Movin' in spectral hues, (በተለዋዋጮ ቀለሞች ውስጥ እቅፍደውር)
황혼의 노래들을 알다 (Songs of dawn meet dusk)
Ringing echoes through the stars, (Tanzen zu den Sternen)
Whispered chants from afar, (सूनी जगहों की मुरमुर)

[Bridge]
Whirlwinds of vibrant speech, (Слово вихрь)
Capture the heart, let it teach, (Magia en cada palabra)
छायाएँ अपने नर्तकियों में संगति करती हैं (Shadows harmonize in their rhythm)
[Verse]
Bailando auf den Flügeln der Luft, (فين السماء?)
Quoi de neuf dans le spiral? (りんかくの中で)
Danza electrica, turntable soul, (छायाएँ छिड़कती)
Espíritu y sonido en Kontroll-Z.

[Chorus]
Groovin' through the languages, (언어가 율동해)
Feel the fusion, cha-cha vibe, (Ritmo dentro de)
World colliding, turn in tune, (世界が回る)
Move with the groove, a symphonie divine.
[Verse 2]
Rhythms weaving in the cosmos, (宇宙の中で)
Caminos de luz y sombras, (빛과 그림자 속에서)
Polyglot beat, flow within, (흐름 속에)
Heartbeats drumming, syncopated dreams.

[Chorus]
Harmony in whispers, (Τα ψιθυρίσματα αρμονίας)
Feel the vibe, a swirling ether, (성군의 소리)
Speak in tongues, dance with the unknown, (उपसर्ग का नृत्य)
[Bridge]
Echoes of time, spirals vast, (विस्तृत सर्पिल)
Murmures dans l'obscurité, (暗闇のささやき)
Threads of sound, boundless weave, (소리의 실, 한계 없는 직조)
World's tapestry, we conceive
(ख्वाबों की चादर)
[Verse 3]
Rivers of bass, pulse with grace, (川のベース)
Clapping shadows, entwined embrace, (影の拍叩き)
Mundo diverso, en un mismo compás, (같은 박자에)
Revolution de la note, en un giroscopio fugaz.
[Chorus]
Melody's revolution, (旋律の革命)
Ride the waves of surreal sound, (Un son symphonique)
[Verse 4]
Breath of beats, wind's gentle caress, (वायु की धड़कन)
Dans les rythmes secrets, (비밀의 리듬 거리)
Orbit of harmonies, (اربيت من التوافق)
旋律的な大海原を漂うこと (Sail on through the melodic seas)

[Chorus]
Interwoven symphony, (交織軌範)
Feel the whispers of quantum sound, (Lugares vibrations son)
